notesc
=====

*Run preproc.sh to add the correct shebang for this system*

This program is intended to compile (Pandoc) markdown documents, university
notes, into PDFs.

usage: notesc.py [-h] [--input [INPUT]] [--output [OUTPUT]] [--prepend [PREPEND ...]]
                 [--template [TEMPLATE]] [--debug]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --input [INPUT], -i [INPUT]
                        Input path. Use '-' or leave blank for stdin
  --output [OUTPUT], -o [OUTPUT]
                        Output path. Use '-' or leave blank for stdout
  --prepend [PREPEND ...], -p [PREPEND ...]
                        Path to file to prepend
  --template [TEMPLATE], -t [TEMPLATE]
                        LaTeX Pandoc template
  --debug               Debug
